      <purpose>To record a suggestion, advice or proposal about the most suitable treatment at a specific time, for each patient affected with glaucoma.</purpose>
      <keywords>advice</keywords>
      <keywords>proposal</keywords>
      <keywords>suggestion</keywords>
      <keywords>glaucoma</keywords>
      <use>Use to record a suggestion, advice or proposal about the treatment of glaucoma, valid at a specific time of healthcare.&#xD;
The statement is considered for the specific point-in-time it is registered, as the therapeutic guidelines may vary according to the context of the disease and the information evaluated in each clinical encounter.&#xD;
For example, the treatment can be modified over time depending on the progression of the disease.</use>
